INSERT INTO `employer` VALUES(918, 'Srei Infrastructure Finance Ltd.', 920, 1, 'Srei Infrastructure Finance Limited has been a pioneer in infrastructure financing in India, steadily contributing towards infrastructural development, and a better tomorrow. Today, we are synonymous with innovative infrastructure financing from customized solutions to marketing programmes.\r\n\r\nIn over 23 years of operation, we have empowered more than 30,000 entrepreneurs through our bouquet of services in the infrastructure sector: Infrastructure Project Finance, Advisory and Development, Infrastructure Equipment Finance, Sahaj e-Village, Venture Capital, Capital Market, QUIPPO - Equipment Bank, VIOM – Telecom Towers and Insurance Broking. \r\n\r\nSrei has led from the forefront in almost all stages of the infrastructure value chain. We are amongst the first Indian NBFCs to access the international market for funds; the first Indian infrastructure NBFC to be listed on the London Stock Exchange; and the first company to lay the ground for passive telecom infrastructure in India.\r\n\r\nWe are also the first to break new ground in rural IT infrastructure in India, under the National e-Governance Plan of the Government of India. This mega project, called Srei Sahaj e-Village, envisages creating over 28,000 Common Service Centres (CSCs) in six states, offering B2B, B2C, G2C and e-Learning services to a 30 crore rural population. \r\n\r\nTo broad base shareholding, Srei was listed on the London Stock Exchange (LSE) way back in 2005. Besides, we have the distinction of international institutions as our stakeholders, including IFC (International Finance Corporation - World Bank Group), KfW & DEG Germany (Financial Institutions owned by the Government of Germany), FMO (Financial Institution owned by the Government of Netherlands), BIO (Financial Institution owned by the Government of Belgium) and FINFUND (Financial Institution owned by the Government of Finland). \r\n\r\nWith a customer base of over 30,000 and over  30,880 crore of Consolidated Assets Under Management, Srei has a pan-India presence with a network of 85 offices. We share a strong partnership with the Tata Group through Viom Networks Limited for shared passive telecom infrastructure and BNP Paribas for Equipment Financing. We are also increasing our presence overseas and currently operate two offices in Russia. Our competitive edge and the ability to provide all possible infrastructure related services under one roof, makes us the most preferred partner for infrastructure players in India\r\n', 'chinmay.rao@srei.com', 1, '639', 'www.srei.com', '', 1, 'Chinmay Rao', '9911747093', 'dbadmin', '2012-09-16 14:56:08', '0', 'SREI Infrastructure Finance Ltd.D-2, 5th Floor, Southern Park, Saket Place, Saket', '110017');
